OL,3,CMother-of-two died after tripping and
OL,4,Cfalling outside hospital entrance
OL,6,FA mother-of-two died three weeks after
OL,7,Ftripping on a metal flap outside a
OL,8,Fhospital, her family has said.
OL,10,FLorna Loxton, a former auxiliary
OL,11,Fnurse, had been at Bristol Royal
OL,12,FInfirmary for a cardiology appointment
OL,13,Fon January 7.
OL,15,FShe began walking to her taxi outside
OL,16,Fthe hospital when her three-wheeled
OL,17,Fwalking frame is believed to have
OL,18,Fbecame lodged in a metal flap which
OL,19,Fcovered a bollard.
