OL,6,FThe 55-year-old tripped as a result,
OL,7,Fbreaking her hip and hitting her head
OL,8,Fon the ground. She underwent surgery
OL,9,Fon her hip but her condition
OL,10,Fdeteriorated and she died in hospital
OL,11,Fon January 28.
OL,13,FHer cause of death has yet to be
OL,14,Fformally established and an inquest
OL,15,Fwill take place on a date to be fixed.
OL,17,FMs Loxton's daughter Danni, 30, and
OL,18,Fson Mark, 35, have paid tribute to
OL,19,Ftheir mother who lived with myotonic
OL,20,Fdystrophy, which causes muscle
OL,21,Fweakness.
