OL,6,FShe was described as an animal lover,
OL,7,Fwho enjoyed riding and caring for
OL,8,Fhorses, as well as looking after her
OL,9,Fthree dogs.
OL,11,FDaughter Danni, an entertainment
OL,12,Fmanager, said: "She couldn't work for
OL,13,Fa lot of years because of her illness,
OL,14,Fsome days she couldn't even get out of
OL,15,Fbed, but she did the very best she
OL,16,Fcould.
