OL,6,F"When she would come and see my shows,
OL,7,Fshe was so proud of me. I will always
OL,8,Fremember how much she loved me and
OL,9,FMark, and how proud she was of him too
OL,10,Ffor being so independent even though
OL,11,Fhe has the same condition she did.
OL,13,F"Mum loved her music ` JLS, for some
OL,14,Freason, and '80s music ` and she
OL,15,Fwatched all the soaps, particularly
OL,16,Fthe Australian ones, and Western films.
OL,18,F"I would speak to her all the time and
OL,19,Fshe lived her life as best she could.
OL,20,FThe way we lost her has been
OL,21,Fabsolutely traumatic."
