OL,6,FMs Loxton's family are being supported
OL,7,Fby law firm Slater and Gordon in their
OL,8,Fsearch for answers about what happened.
OL,10,FSamantha Griffiths, senior associate
OL,11,Fat Slater and Gordon, said: "This was
OL,12,Fan absolutely tragic incident and has
OL,13,Fleft Danni and Mark absolutely
OL,14,Fdevastated ` not just with the loss of
OL,15,Ftheir beloved mother, but particularly
OL,16,Fthe manner in which it happened.
