OL,6,F"Hospitals should be one of the safest
OL,7,Fpossible environments for people with
OL,8,Fmobility problems who use mobility
OL,9,Faids, but this has been far from the
OL,10,Fcase in Lorna's situation.
OL,12,F"We will support Lorna's family in
OL,13,Fevery way possible to get the answers
OL,14,Fthey need and deserve around her
OL,15,Fdeath."
