OL,6,FThe law firm said a report from
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals Bristol and
OL,8,FWeston NHS Foundation Trust found the
OL,9,Fbollard posts were not being monitored
OL,10,Fby the estates and facilities team
OL,11,Fwhen Ms Loxton died.
OL,13,FIt described the angle of the metal
OL,14,Fflat as a "trip hazard", Slater and
OL,15,FGordon said.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for University
OL,18,FHospitals Bristol and Weston NHS
OL,19,FFoundation Trust said: "We would like
OL,20,Fto offer our heartfelt condolences to
OL,21,FLorna's family.
